snippet.title: Aleks Svetski on Personal Responsibility, Self Sovereignty, and Personal Empowerment
snippet.description:
Aleks' Medium:
https://t.co/OP8RDTQcot?amp=1

Amber App: 
https://amber.app/

Support me on Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/Tucsonblockchain

Donate Bitcoin to Tucson Blockchain:
https://btcpay734546.lndyn.com/apps/3UdYE4JjSGHbBqvgxBXuwJafb9yH/crowdfund

I am not a financial advisor and instead try to take the route of educating individuals so that they can make informed decisions with their money on their own. If you take anything I say as financial advice, that's on you because I am not offering financial advice, but instead education. I do not discourage the use of a licensed professional but instead encourage individuals to empower themselves when it comes to money.
